{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act29side", "eventName": "崔林特爾梅之金", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "ZT-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "夜歌“未見的高塔”", "storyInfo": "薇薇安娜走在無盡的螺旋樓梯上，看到了不同的命運可能性。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別站在外面，快進來呀。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以帶你參觀我的房間。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g6_towerterrace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_animal_loop", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣怎麼樣？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是你自己布置的嗎？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷奧妮也有幫忙啦。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很大，很明亮。薇薇安……你的房間真漂亮。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#8$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝！", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#6$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是整座高塔採光最好的房間，雖然施彤領的太陽老是偷懶不願意出來，但哪怕是陰天，待在裡面也不會覺得太暗。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有這個露台！它佔了房間的一整面側牆，視野可棒了……你往遠處看，看到了嗎？", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到什麼？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個綠色的屋頂！", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格魯加西植物館。媽媽帶我去過幾次，裡面種了好多好多施彤領甚至萊塔尼亞都沒有的植物。但我最喜歡它的屋頂。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾株玻利瓦爾的鉤藤爬上了屋頂，估計是太高了很難清理，工作人員就一直任由它生長，久而久之把屋頂都蓋住啦！", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "春天的時候，鉤藤開滿了淡粉色的花簇，整片屋頂看過去是淡粉色的，就像一朵雲；現在是夏天，你看，它是很深的綠色……", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鉤藤的葉子不會凋落，等到了秋天，屋頂又會變成金燦燦的；而進入冬天後，則只剩下乾乾淨淨的白色。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，能想像得到，很美。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前，爸爸的政務再忙，也會每天抽出時間來這裡。媽媽在旁邊描繪面前的風景，他就悄悄跟我講他和媽媽的故事。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸媽媽的故事，可以講給我聽嗎？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天在金盞花小巷，爸爸等到了媽媽？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（點頭）", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸說，那天他下定決心跟媽媽告別。可見到她的瞬間，他根本無法允許自己就那麼轉身離開……", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“小薇薇安，如果愛人的手本能相牽，何故放任山水將它們分隔？！”嘖，真肉麻！總之爸爸帶著媽媽回到了施彤領。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸就站在……喏，塔下的那個位置，對著長輩和言臣說，如果不承認媽媽的身份，他便永不進入霍赫貝格家族的高塔！", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更不會繼任選帝侯。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些貴族妥協了？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為爸爸真的在塔下站了三天……好多人來勸他，也有罵他的，都沒有成功，最後只能放棄啦。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#9$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沃爾納·馮·霍赫貝格保護了他的愛人，像文學作品裡面的英雄那樣。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們結成了婚姻，並且得到了所有人的祝福。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜·霍赫貝格，你的降生也得到了所有人的祝福。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真好啊。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你說什麼？", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#10$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "薇薇安娜。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這樣的生活，真好啊。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是雷奧妮嗎？門沒有關。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "侍女走了進來，薇薇安娜想要躲避，但對方徑直走向了身旁的小女孩，像是沒有看見她。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷奧妮，你是來拿走這塊地毯的嗎？", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，薇薇安娜小姐，請您往旁邊借過一下。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是米諾斯匠人的特級工藝品，赤腳踩上去超舒服的，上面的白牆和湖泊栩栩如生，像是真的有風繞在腳邊吹。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽很喜歡這塊地毯，當時為了買下它，打了很久的工，還替別人代筆寫了很多詩。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽當年離開崔林特爾梅的時候，沒有多少行李，但特地帶上了這塊地毯。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……所以它還能賣一些錢。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要理解夫人。這座高塔已經空了，這個漂亮的大房間，是它最後剩下的體面。不到萬不得已，夫人不會去動這裡面的東西。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但沃爾納老爺死後，夫人一直疲於和各種人周旋，家裡能變賣的都變賣了……", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您馬上就要去哥倫比亞讀書了，需要的開銷不算小，夫人希望您在異國他鄉能不用吃苦。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，我可以、我可以不去的。", "name": "薇薇安"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，您應該離開施彤領，離開萊塔尼亞，薇薇安娜小姐。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夫人兩年前就向選帝侯提了這件事，但直到最近才讓他點了頭，您還是儘早啟程比較好，萬一選帝侯反悔……", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那媽媽呢，媽媽還是不能陪我去嗎？", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#5$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夫人得讓選帝侯能隨時看到她，她必須留在這座高塔裡。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我想去求求切爾德叔叔。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#4$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜小姐，切爾德是您的堂叔，但他更是施彤領現在的選帝侯……", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年沃爾納老爺即位選帝侯才兩年，就在巡視的路途中遇刺身亡，他和夫人的婚姻已經得罪了許多人，人們都在猜是切爾德……", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我糊塗了，我跟您說這個做什麼！", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……雷奧妮，我有個問題，不知道該去問誰才好。", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#2$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果，如果爸爸媽媽能過上普普通通的生活，我們是不是就能一直幸福了？", "name": "薇薇安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#4$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1121_1#4$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1121_1#4$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜小姐……您一直都是個懂事的孩子。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去收拾行李吧。您心愛的書本和畫冊，可以裝進那個小藤條箱子裡。我處理完這塊地毯，再回來整理其他的東西。", "name": "雷奧妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_497_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空空的風聲。埃拉菲亞女孩望向露台外的城市。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論什麼季節，格魯加西植物館的屋頂再漂亮，在暗下來的天色裡，又怎麼能看得清呢？"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.0, "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅小姐，阿爾圖羅小姐？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我好像，真的聽不見那些聲音了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.0, "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身上沒有明顯的傷口。難道是聽力受到了干擾嗎？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。只是覺得很安靜，我有些不習慣……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕此刻您就站在我面前，我依然感覺……您離我特別遙遠。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？這樣有沒有好一點？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說話要不要更大聲點？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒、沒有關係。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我帶你到旁邊休息一下吧，追你的人應該已經走遠了。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，我幫你拿著琴。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼抓得這麼緊啊，手指都發白了！", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這把琴對你來說一定很重要。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是我的眼睛、耳朵和喉舌，是我的心臟。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是說來慚愧，我曾經，對它感到懼怕。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#10$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我花了很長的時間，才學會怎樣和它相處。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g8_laterano_dwelling", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1120_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，為什麼不開燈縮在角落裡？盧恰娜嬸嬸都不知道你回來了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天在公園，我們划完船後，你不是去練琴了嗎？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_kickviolin", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯，對不起，我好像踢到了你的琴。這件樂器很珍貴，如果損壞的話……我有一些錢，可以用來賠償。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1120_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費迪，幫我把它拿到房間外面去好不好？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1120_1#9$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以把它藏起來，書房、閣樓、儲藏室……哪裡都可以。或者，或者直接丟掉……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1120_1#9$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在哭嗎？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你又演奏自己沒有掌握的曲子了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1120_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道，費迪……只要一拉響它的弦，我就能聽見很多很多聲音。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1120_1#2$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些聲音很真實，它們被關在大人們的身體裡面了。它們想要出來，我應該幫它們。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1120_1#2$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1120_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是它們太大聲，太嘈雜了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1120_1#9$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼多聲音在哭，那麼多聲音在笑，那麼多聲音在竊竊私語，那麼多聲音在憤憤地抱怨……它們一齊湧過來……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1120_1#9$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1120_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吵！費迪，我快要喘不過氣了——", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1120_1#4$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該是生病了。需要我去叫盧恰娜嬸嬸嗎？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1120_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費迪，我只是需要，需要安靜……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1120_1#3$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1118_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "房間裡沒有人再說話，只剩下角落裡極低極低的啜泣聲。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隔著一段距離，兩頂黑色的光環相對著發出幽幽的光。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "安靜一會兒就好，讓我的腦袋沒那麼痛，就一會兒。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我會適應那些聲音的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我只是，還沒有掌握方法……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "白天不也很快就學會了划船嗎？只要穿過那片濃霧，就能到達湖心的島嶼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "有歌聲穿過湖面。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是您在唱歌嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實是這條街上的流浪歌手愛唱的小調啦。嘿，本來很好聽的，但我有點五音不全……", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前揚在外面受了欺負跑回家，悶著頭不說話的時候，我也是這麼安慰他的。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝您。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您剛剛說，“這條街”？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯啊。卡爾·施密特街，崔林特爾梅的人也叫它金盞花小巷。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g1_marigold", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$higherdimensionalspaces_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤利婭女士，你還沒有回答我的問題。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據崔林特爾梅憲兵隊的記錄，1085年秋，芬恩男爵在卡爾·施密特街為了制止一起誘拐犯罪，與嫌疑人展開了激烈戰鬥。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男爵受傷暈倒，等他醒來時，嫌疑人與被誘拐的卡普里尼女性，二十七歲的尤利婭·許勒爾，一同失去了下落。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛里斯·博爾丁主動接過了這個案子，他展開了一系列調查，但沒有得到任何有效線索。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他判定男爵的證詞存在蹊蹺，唯有一件事情可以確定：男爵是最後一個見到你的人。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他堅信這其中存在某種隱秘。就像巫王晚年的法術實驗之於感染者平民，而你成了男爵的目標。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但迫於上層的壓力，憲兵隊叫停了後續調查，以“意外失蹤”結案。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛里斯·博爾丁將卷宗帶回了自己的住所，十五年來，它一直在變厚。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他從未放棄調查真相，也從未放棄尋找你的下落。儘管種種線索表明：尤利婭·許勒爾，已經死亡。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你剛剛告訴我，這裡是卡爾·施密特街。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換言之，出於某些原因，你在死亡後意外來到了“始源之角”，並以“意識體”的形式存在。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你的認知中，你一直沒有離開過當年的案發現場。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼請告訴我，當年究竟發生了什麼？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡確實就是金盞花小巷。我們正站在街口的鋼琴教室前。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，執行者先生，已經耽誤很多時間了。我得趕快把這些法術裝置放到指定的位置上去！", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些戴面具的傢伙，應該很快就會出現了。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的意思是，巫王殘黨會按照某種規律出現在荒域的各處？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#7$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，他們是巫王殘黨嗎？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，並非現實中以巫王之名活躍的作亂者。您經常見到的，應該是巫王術式的具象化，真正的“赫爾昏佐倫的餘音”。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……循音覓跡，便能見到巫王。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫王為什麼也在崔林特爾梅？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過也是。我已經死了，巫王也死了，我們在同一個地方，也很正常。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這些奇怪的現象反倒解釋得通了……", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許是失去了樂聲的緣故，我無法感知到您眼中的一切。您為何稱呼這裡為“崔林特爾梅”？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你也看不見嗎？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅小姐，你能不能看到前面的樂器塔？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樂器塔？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅順著卡普里尼女性手指的方向看去，遠處除了一片曖昧的光影，別無他物。"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g11_thronesworld", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帝國音樂學院的樂器塔，但只有十一座。", "name": "尤利婭"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帝國音樂學院是巴赫區最著名的地標建築。學院每一座高塔的設計靈感都來自於一種樂器，並在建成的時候直接以此命名。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它本身便擁有十一種樂器，巴赫先生主持“光榮首都計劃”時，又補充了十一種。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十二座樂器高塔，對應著崔林特爾梅的二十二個城區，如同一支完美的交響樂團。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，你果然知道。", "name": "尤利婭"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，十一座樂器塔，那不是崔林特爾梅的帝國音樂學院，而是巫王時代的帝國音樂學院。", "name": "尤利婭"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有我們身後的方向……是一座傾斜的玉色圓形高塔。", "name": "尤利婭"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“永恆斜塔”？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本是某位選帝侯的高塔，因為地層變化，日漸傾斜，在高塔術師超級法陣的支援下，它保持著極其驚人的傾斜角度而不倒。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個萊塔尼亞建築史上的奇蹟，在四百年前毀於一場天災……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不止不止。還有“維恩大鐘樓”、“倒懸的懲戒樓”、“知識之門”、“天象之樓”、“美泉塔”……", "name": "尤利婭"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成千上萬座不同時代、不同形制、不同功用的高塔，我只在書上見過，在老人們的故事裡聽過……", "name": "尤利婭"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它們統統矗立在這裡。", "name": "尤利婭"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡不是崔林特爾梅，也不是維杜尼亞，它最準確的稱呼只能是……“萊塔尼亞”。", "name": "尤利婭"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我唯一熟悉的只有腳下這條金盞花小巷，街口是鋼琴教室，街尾是畫廊，正中間是我的咖啡館……", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好還在，我重新找到了它們。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以前怎樣生活，現在依然這樣生活。所以雖然這裡無比陌生，我還是習慣叫它“崔林特爾梅”。", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，並非您重新找到了熟悉的生活。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而是因為您的生活本身，您才能來到這裡。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_collapse", "volume": 0.5, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 60.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_statueshake", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_statuecollapse", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帝國音樂學院的樂器塔只剩下九座了……鋼琴塔和圓號塔什麼時候不見的？", "name": "尤利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（弗萊蒙特閣下說得沒錯，“始源之角”正在加速崩毀……）", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1